WEBVTT

00:04:29.855 --> 00:04:31.022
My answer?

00:04:31.046 --> 00:04:35.023
"Blockbuster. BlackBerry.
Polaroid. Toys 'R' Us.

00:04:35.047 --> 00:04:36.513
Do you want me to keep going?"

00:04:37.301 --> 00:04:40.348
So how do you shake things up
before it's too late?

00:04:40.992 --> 00:04:44.395
For that, we're going to the movies.

00:04:44.419 --> 00:04:47.228
(Music)

00:04:47.252 --> 00:04:50.658
In 1999, Warner Brothers
released the first animated movie

00:04:50.682 --> 00:04:52.521
directed by Brad Bird:

00:04:52.545 --> 00:04:53.881
"Iron Giant."

00:04:53.905 --> 00:04:56.484
John Walker: I remember being
so excited about it.

00:04:56.508 --> 00:04:59.024
AG: This is Brad's producer, John Walker.

00:04:59.048 --> 00:05:02.000
It was the first big project
for both Brad and John.